    <endEvent id="endEvent_urgencies" name="Referral to Emergency">
      <documentation>Red Flags present → immediate referral to the Emergency Visit (template "Visita URG"). According to the client schema, for the POC it is not necessary to create another Folder + Templates: the emergency visit falls outside the POC Lumbalgia Templates Folder.</documentation>
      <extensionElements>
        <design:stencilid><![CDATA[EndTerminateEvent]]></design:stencilid>
        <design:display_ref_in_diagram><![CDATA[true]]></design:display_ref_in_diagram>
      </extensionElements>
      <terminateEventDefinition></terminateEventDefinition>
    </endEvent>
    <endEvent id="endEvent_yellowFlagsPathway" name="Process Abort">
      <documentation>Yellow Flags present (without Red Flags) → care pathway PENDING ADJUSTMENT with the client. Common options: referral to Pain Unit, psychosocial intervention, active physiotherapy with cognitive component, proactive follow-up in primary care. This End event is a placeholder replaceable by a specific subprocess when defined.</documentation>
      <extensionElements>
        <design:stencilid><![CDATA[EndTerminateEvent]]></design:stencilid>
        <design:display_ref_in_diagram><![CDATA[true]]></design:display_ref_in_diagram>
      </extensionElements>
      <terminateEventDefinition></terminateEventDefinition>
    </endEvent>
    <endEvent id="endEvent_processCompleted" name="Process Completed">
      <extensionElements>
        <design:stencilid><![CDATA[EndTerminateEvent]]></design:stencilid>
        <design:display_ref_in_diagram><![CDATA[true]]></design:display_ref_in_diagram>
      </extensionElements>
      <terminateEventDefinition></terminateEventDefinition>
    </endEvent>
