        <design:text><![CDATA[IN: ehrId-> OpenEHR patient identifier
IN: codeClinicalProcessName -> Clinical Process Code
IN: codeProcessType -> Process Code within the Clinical Process
IN: processDefinition -> Definition of Process within the Clinical Process
IN: admistrativeComposition_hier_object_id-> Identifies the Administrative Composition of the indicated Type
IN: original_hier_object_id-> Id Composition Reason for Encounter

OUT: idInstanciaProceso-> Business Process Identifier

]]></design:text>
